author: senh
title: Luggage-Shipping Services Give Fliers Options
text:
Portland Oregonian , Friday - 08/14/2015 - 09:00 AM 
The Bayfront, aquarium and the hospitable Whaler motel make a find end-of-summer getaway. Sleep-deprived, medicated, suicidal and armed: Federal air marshals in disarray CNN , Friday - 08/14/2015 - 07:52 AM 
It was just before 3 a.m. on July 31, 2013, when a federal law enforcement officer left Room 634 of the Sheraton Syracuse University Hotel, stood underneath a flagpole, put a gun to his head and pulled the trigger. The single shell casing landed near a bench next to his body.
